<plot>"Your Heart" all too literally takes us on the journey of a broken heart. A young woman whose heart has been ripped out (and chewed on, run over, buried with, played with, etc.) shows us that although the pain can become unbearable at times, we can slowly begin the healing process and, though we have our fears and our doubts, we can find the strength inside to move on, and possibly, to love again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?667524</url></doc>
